            ul 
                li We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you:
                    ul
                        li Fill out a form on our website
                        li Complete a lead generation form via LinkedIn
                <br>
                li This information may include:
                    ul
                        li Your name
                        li Email address
                        li Phone number
                        li Company name
                        li Job title
                        li Any additional information you choose to share

            h2 2. How We Use Your Information
            ul 
                li To respond to inquiries or requests made through our website or LinkedIn forms
                li To send you relevant information, updates, or offers related to our services
                li To improve our website and marketing strategies
                li To follow up on lead generation efforts and provide customized services
